like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"見過d咩泳客走光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4697cad82a7f5e939640478809d023fd00b2920","tid":15633,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無試過裸泳<br />\n有無見過人賴屎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旅行去馬爾代夫就試過裸泳<br />\n返工時間梗係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有, 尤其係細路<br />\n耐唔時會係泳池柯屎, 唔知係佢忍唔住定玩野啦"},{"pid":"9f1c069e9374d98449797f08ab3b602442f54a8e","tid":15633,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見過d咩泳客走光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見過個大陸妹就咁著件防曬衣落水<br />\n入面冇著其他野, 飛晒釘"},{"pid":"938086e019f9eea7f5c916c1cd0a63f0dbeeb69b","tid":15633,"uid":44582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b48b890659b2e629481a7ed3fdb5d86f849fbb4","tid":15633,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:02:21.000Z","msg":"巴打一定好fit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e67b46ab5211a2b055bdc84bade6e950bcf475","tid":15633,"uid":44582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:02:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇撞過鬼？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講東涌果邊d盤好猛"},{"pid":"ec4fdd4a64a0114428e2039c8bcf8b5e2c24c7cb","tid":15633,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi