"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>矮仔學咩人做救生員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我 192"},{"pid":"71a049307da113bfc4df241e3fe22e55bbdda4e3","tid":15633,"uid":14457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>番過咩西池同天堂池<br />\n<br />\n最多一日試過搵幾多<br />\n<br />\n之前on9番過比華利山<br />\n會所個位望住我地<br />\n話有休息位<br />\n點解係個雜物房黎<br />\n住客都入得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係拎黎放袋<br />\n番左一日無番<br />\n不過d 姐姐都幾正</blockquote><br />\n老實講有會所大部分都西池<br />\n會所班人由朝check 到晚<br />\n不過又唔怪得佢地<br />\n都係源自好多西客投訴<br />\n<br />\n天堂池就半山區都係架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人游又hea 由朝打機打到晚<br />\n另外室內池都好好返 起碼唔洗曬同餵蚊<br />\n試過頂一次急更 有 1000蚊一日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n番過個室內池又焗又熱<br />\n大部分玻璃 d 陽光透哂落黎<br />\n抽風又廢 兩三點個時d 水蒸氣一出<br />\n好似蒸魚咁<br />\n仲要上台 之前都好似話試過有師兄焗到中暑<br />\n之後先有幾部風機頂頂<br />\n<br />\n1100都見過 諗住等佢1200先報<br />\n因為之前都見過佢報1200 點知比人1100 都有人報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 你點解可以頂到九年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f271a1ff734181ef09d14663f1060744cb17ee","tid":15633,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:02:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>番過咩西池同天堂池<br />\n<br />\n最多一日試過搵幾多<br />\n<br />\n之前on9番過比華利山<br />\n會所個位望住我地<br />\n話有休息位<br />\n點解係個雜物房黎<br />\n住客都入得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係拎黎放袋<br />\n番左一日無番<br />\n不過d 姐姐都幾正</blockquote><br />\n老實講有會所大部分都西池<br />\n會所班人由朝check 到晚<br />\n不過又唔怪得佢地<br />\n都係源自好多西客投訴<br />\n<br />\n天堂池就半山區都係架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人游又hea 由朝打機打到晚<br />\n另外室內池都好好返 起碼唔洗曬同餵蚊<br />\n試過頂一次急更 有 1000蚊一日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n番過個室內池又焗又熱<br />\n大部分玻璃 d 陽光透哂落黎<br />\n抽風又廢 兩三點個時d 水蒸氣一出<br />\n好似蒸魚咁<br />\n仲要上台 之前都好似話試過有師兄焗到中暑<br />\n之後先有幾部風機頂頂<br />\n<br />\n1100都見過 諗住等佢1200先報<br />\n因為之前都見過佢報1200 點知比人1100 都有人報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 你點解可以頂到九年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n9年都唔係日日返足<br />\n讀書時期 16歲就開始當返parttime 咁<br />\n斷斷續續做到而家囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b3041b08f737d8dfcbb520e75b92d4792d740c","tid":15633,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:05:33.000Z","msg":"搵幾多"},{"pid":"918c4605f4b08ba3b061e3df6ed8e90c99cabc43","tid":15633,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勤力返可以一個月 2皮以上"},{"pid":"8eb8e7b1b16ee726096fcaa4036dcc6ce190d5ef","tid":15633,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"巴打有無做沙灘，係咪無泳池咁悶"},{"pid":"7d5b03dfd4bfe3f96b0ff2aff2e445b4d0cf734e","tid":15633,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有無做沙灘，係咪無泳池咁悶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沙灘多啲比堅尼望呀嘛<br />\n又有得玩下艇<br />\n見仁見智啦<br />\n我就覺得泳池就舒服啲"},{"pid":"797df659f2a92453c8c6d0ce8d59cf1d04f18dd6","tid":15633,"uid":20130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>矮仔學咩人做救生員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我 192</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁條J幾長？"},{"pid":"78557f9da25615ac7d50683f319b1eb86d7bfd52","tid":15633,"uid":44582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal